<section class="mb-8">
<h2 class="text-gray-800 text-xl font-semibold leading-tight mb-3">Issue Description</h2>
<p class="text-gray-700 text-base leading-relaxed">
                War refugees often lack verifiable identification, hindering access to essential services and aid. This challenge focuses on creating a secure, decentralized digital ID system using blockchain technology. The system should be user-friendly, protect privacy, and be easily verifiable by relevant organizations.
              </p>
</section>
<section class="mb-8">
<h2 class="text-gray-800 text-xl font-semibold leading-tight mb-3">Impact</h2>
<p class="text-gray-700 text-base leading-relaxed">
                A robust digital ID system can significantly improve the lives of war refugees by enabling access to humanitarian aid, healthcare, education, and financial services. It can also streamline registration processes for asylum and resettlement, and help prevent identity theft and fraud.
              </p>
</section>
<section class="mb-8">
<h2 class="text-gray-800 text-xl font-semibold leading-tight mb-3">Affected Communities</h2>
<p class="text-gray-700 text-base leading-relaxed">
                This issue directly affects war refugees, displaced populations, and aid organizations. Solutions will also benefit host governments and international bodies working to manage refugee crises and provide support.
              </p>
</section>
<div class="mb-8 flex justify-start">
<button class="flex items-center justify-center rounded-full h-11 px-6 bg-[#d2e2f3] text-gray-800 text-sm font-bold leading-normal tracking-[0.015em] hover:bg-opacity-80 transition-all duration-200">
